content.raw:
I regenerated the dat file but surprised to find that it’s the same as the existing one. I verified the result against the new .dot file and the comms seem to be correct. The yellow tile in the middle in the screenshot below is tile 4 in the dot graph. If it were connected to the straight tile \(tile 17\) to its right then the straight tile would be lit. But in this case, the straight tile is not lit which shows correctly that there are no connections between them. Interesting..

![](data/bitbucket.org/repo/8ze6Mjd/images/310332949-urban_qual_dat2.jpg)
‌
